song_lyrics: Bāluḍe vesh māthe shobhe chhe kesh,
Vahālo rame chhe māro bāluḍe vesh ...°ṭek
Nāth kare chhe līlā Nandjīne nes.... Vahālo° 1
Jenā mahimāno pār pāme na sheṣh... Vahālo° 2
Dekhī pankhīne māro Shyām ḍare chhe,
Dhyān dhare chhe jenu Shivajī hammesh... Vahālo° 3
title: Bāluḍe vesh māthe shobhe chhe kesh
